es of collective\nintelligence to advance its current capabilities. We hope this review can serve\nas a bridge between the complex systems and deep learning communities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Nov 2021 08:39:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Dec 2021 22:02:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 10 Mar 2022 14:25:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-11"}
